spirit:component.spirit:name: cont_microblaze_mdm_1_0

spirit:field.spirit:name: RX FIFO Valid Data
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates if the receive FIFO has valid data: 0 - Receive FIFO is empty. 1 - Receive FIFO has valid data.

spirit:field.spirit:name: RX FIFO Full
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates if the receive FIFO is full: 0 - Receive FIFO is not full. 1 - Receive FIFO is full.

spirit:field.spirit:name: TX FIFO Empty
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates if the transmit FIFO is empty: 0 - Transmit FIFO is not empty. 1 - Transmit FIFO is empty.

spirit:field.spirit:name: TX FIFO Full
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates if the transmit FIFO is full: 0 - Transmit FIFO is not full. 1 - Transmit FIFO is full.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Interrupt Enabled
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates that interrupt is enabled: 0 - Interrupt is disabled. 1 - Interrupt is enabled.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Reset TX FIFO
spirit:field.spirit:description: Reset/clear the transmit FIFO: 0 - Do nothing. 1 - Clear the transmit FIFO.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Reset RX FIFO
spirit:field.spirit:description: Reset/clear the receive FIFO: 0 - Do nothing. 1 - Clear the receive FIFO.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Clear EXT_BRK
spirit:field.spirit:description: Clear the EXT_BRK signal set by JTAG: 0 - Do nothing. 1 - Clear the signal.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Interrupt Enabled
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates interrupt for the MDM JTAG UART: 0 - Disable interrupt interrupt. 1 - Enable interrupt signal.

spirit:field.spirit:name: LOCK
spirit:field.spirit:description: Indicates the access lock status: 0 - The lock is not acquired. 1 - The lock has been acquired by the JTAG interface.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Bit Size
spirit:field.spirit:description: Number of bits in the accessed debug register - 1

spirit:field.spirit:name: Access MDM
spirit:field.spirit:description: Access MDM or MicroBlaze Debug register: 0 - MicroBlaze debug register access. 1 - MDM debug register access.

spirit:field.spirit:name: Access Lock Type
spirit:field.spirit:description: Access lock type write: 0 - Release access lock to abort atomic sequence. 1 - Lock before first access and unlock after last. 2 - Lock before first access, otherwise keep lock. 3 - Force lock acquisition, even if aquired by JTAG.

spirit:field.spirit:name: DBG Data
spirit:field.spirit:description: Read or write debug register data indicated by DBG_CTRL.

spirit:field.spirit:name: DBG_LOCK
spirit:field.spirit:description: Unlock access to registers DBG_CTLR and DBG_DATA when writing 0xEBAB.
